title: 11/06/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 11/06/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On Today's DP Show, DP recaps last night's game between the Packers and Niners. Was Devante Adams comment about being the best Wideout in the game taken out of context? We're joined by legendary broadcaster Brent Musberger and Pro Football Talk's Mike Florio. Plus, the guys have some fun with a caller.
